# for Raspberry Pi 1 Revision 2
#
#       Physical pins
# (as labeled on the board)     GPIO_PIN number to use 
#       2                               0
#       3                               1
#       4                               2
#       7                               3
#       8                               4
#       9                               5
#       10                              6
